Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\shad0\bord2\frz1.5\fs34\t(\fs32)\move(364.797,35,364.797,54,24,7323)\c&&HC9D4D7&}Warning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Viewers Sitting in Front of the Television,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:05.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the guys that appear in this anime are delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:07.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So, please do not imitate what you see in this anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:09.98,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnAveria Sans\b1\i0\bord0\blur0.3\fad(450,0)\c&HDADADA&\fs33\pos(362.532,49)}Do not imitate{\i1\fs40}!{\i0\fs33} Or this will happen{\i1\fs40}!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}僕が泣いているのは とても悔しいからです
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)\an8}Boku ga naite iru no wa totemo kuyashii kara desu
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.83,0:00:23.79,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(250,350)}The reason I am crying is\Nbecause I am very frustrated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.21,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}人の尊さやさしさ 踏みにじられそうで
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.21,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Hito no toutosa yasashisa fuminijiraresou de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:29.21,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}I feel as though the nobility and\Nkindness of man is being trampled
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}力を示す者達は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:31.88,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Chikara o shimesu mono tachi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}しなやかさを失って
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:34.51,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Shinayakasa o ushinatte
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:34.51,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Those who show their strength lose their grace
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}ウソまみれドロまみれ じれったい風景でしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uso-mamire doro-mamire jirettai fuukei desho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.51,0:00:40.06,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Covered in dirt and lies, isn't it a vexing sight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}より強くしたたかに タフな生き方をしましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Yori tsuyoku shitataka ni tafu na ikikata o shimashou
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:45.35,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's live more strongly, fiercely, and tougher
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}まっすぐ歩きましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Massugu arukimasho
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:47.61,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Let's walk straight
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}風は向かい風
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kaze wa mukai kaze
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.61,0:00:51.99,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The wind is against us
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ どけ どけ 後ろめたい奴はどけ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke doke doke ushirometai yatsu wa doke
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:58.83,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, move, move, those with\Na guilty conscience, move aside
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}有象無象の町に 灯りをともせ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Uzoumuzou no machi ni akari o tomose
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.83,0:01:03.45,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Light up the town of riffraff
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}どけ そこ どけ 真実のお通りだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Doke soko doke shinjitsu no otouri da
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.00,0:01:08.92,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}Move, make way, truth is coming through
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}正義の時代がくるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Seigi no jidai ga kuru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:11.84,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}The era of justice will come
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}希望の歌もあるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)\an8}Kibou no uta mo aru sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:14.55,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fade(350,350)}There are songs of hope too
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}僕の命この世に 捧げてしまっていいさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)\an8}Boku no inochi kono yo ni sasagete-shimatte ii sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:20.39,OP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(350,500)}I would happily sacrifice my life for this world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:41.74,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\pos(354.601,391)}Yutaka Takenouchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.19,0:01:36.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,My name is Yutaka Takenouchi. I'm 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:38.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm currently commanding
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.47,0:01:41.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,the Year 1 guys at Cromartie High School as their boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.45,0:01:44.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm Yutaka Takenouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:48.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't it my turn to show up yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.92,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\fnVAG Rounded BT\frz356\fs22\b0\shad0\be0\bord0.1\blur0.2\c&H74544C&\pos(352.335,147)\3c&H74544C&\frx16\fry18}Restroom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.92,0:01:52.21,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\pos(317.215,60)\fs60\b0\fnMTF Playtime\shad0\bord0.1\be1\c&H303031&\3c&H303031&}September
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:54.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Year 1 students' monthly meeting\N at Destrade Technical High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:59.05,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\an7\fad(0,300)\fs24\fnJust The Way You Are\shad0\bord0.2\blur0.6\b0\c&H4C513E&\frz3\3c&H5F6F63&\t(\fs30)\move(317.215,96,313.816,84,0,6035)}Defeat\N{\frz4}Cromartie{\frz5} High{\frz6} School
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.63,0:01:58.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The agenda is, "How can we crush\NCromartie High School?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.26,0:02:00.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Noboru Yamaguchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.14,0:02:07.31,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,392)}Noboru Yamaguchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.85,0:02:02.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Due to his invincible strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:07.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}he is called the "Silent Unsinkable Battleship"\Nand leads the Year 1 students at Destrade High.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.31,0:02:11.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At the same time, the motorcycle gang\Nnamed "Earth, Wind, Fire, and Water"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:14.15,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,is also under this man's command.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:17.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,However, not only is he strong in fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:20.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,he is also a man who, in fact,\Nis particular about comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.24,0:02:24.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,However, no one knows about this fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.24,0:02:30.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In other words, in fighting, if you\Ngain control of the head, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.92,0:02:35.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then that means all we need to do is put\Nthe squeeze on Cromartie's Takenouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's right. That's exactly what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:44.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, who's Takenouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:47.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Takenouchi is the head of Cro-High!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.64,0:02:49.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At least remember his name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"By the way, who's Takenouchi?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:57.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Sakamoto, you just told a funny joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:02.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But sadly, he hasn't noticed\Nhis sense of humor himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.87,0:03:05.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, he's what they call a "space case."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:12.79,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,477)}But if you learn to do it on purpose,\Nyou could be considered successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:14.54,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord0.2\blur0.1\fad(600,0)\fnGilles' Comic Font\pos(367.063,370)\fs36\shad0\bord0\c&HECEAEE&}In comedy, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:17.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The point is that since they're acting cocky,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.63,0:03:21.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,they won't know who's boss\N until we put a good squeeze on them once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.09,0:03:25.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,After all, whether it's fighting or a woman's\Ncrotch, it's best to put a good squeeze on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ishikawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:31.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't make us laugh at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.35,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:33.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.32,0:03:37.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Ishikawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.03,0:03:41.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ishikawa, are you all right? Snap out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:45.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't tell stupid jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.12,0:03:47.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That's what you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:50.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi hates comedy and jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:54.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Wrong! There's no one\N who loves comedy more than I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.79,0:03:56.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Why did I hit Ishikawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.71,0:04:00.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's because he chose to tell\Nsex jokes without thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.26,0:04:04.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is the typical pattern that someone\Nwith no sense of humor quickly falls into.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And for laughing, the rest of you are also guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:09.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The most dangerous thing is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:12.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,that this kind of guy sometimes debuts\Nprofessionally when he isn't good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.81,0:04:15.90,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,In a way, it leads to comedians\Nlowering their standards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:19.44,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,If, by some mistake,\N he appears on a TV show,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'll change the channel without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:24.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's discuss things seriously now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:28.58,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah. First question is how to get\Ninto Cromartie High School.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:32.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You say get in, but it wouldn't be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Guys at Cromartie are really crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,When push comes to shove, they kill without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:42.55,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That Takenouchi guy in particular\Ncan't be stopped once he snaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:46.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How can we get into Cromartie easily?\NThat's the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.01,0:04:47.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Geez, idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:50.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Isn't there at least one person\Nwho tries to make us laugh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Read the mood in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:56.77,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's stupid how you keep saying "Cromartie,\NCromartie," as if that's the only word you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:05:00.23,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Are you all villagers of\NCromartie Village?", I'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:01.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:04.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This joke is funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi is thinking deeply about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.82,0:05:11.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Cromartie is\N too big to deal with, as we feared?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.12,0:05:16.04,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I want to tell this joke to everyone so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:19.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But if I did that, I'd plunge\Nfrom my current position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:21.50,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Besides, I'm considered\N to be a reserved person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.30,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But this joke can only be used now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:27.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It would be too late after we attack Cro-High.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.60,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, I've decided!\NI'll quit being the boss as of today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:35.81,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The only reason I've been acting as the boss\Nwas because I was good at fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:38.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but that was a big mistake to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.65,0:05:40.86,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't make people laugh,\Neven with this hairstyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.86,0:05:49.24,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What I really want to do is tell lots of\N funny jokes and make everyone bust out laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:52.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,All right then, I'll announce\Nthis joke to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:56.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The only thing I can do after that is pray\Nthat the God of Comedy blesses me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.83,0:05:58.71,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:01.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep\Ntalking about meaningless stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:05.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I've been listening to what you're saying,\Nand the meeting hasn't progressed at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:08.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's stupid how you keep saying "Cromartie,\NCromartie" as if that's the only word you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:11.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"Are you all villagers of Cromartie Village?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:13.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:20.27,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You see?! Yamaguchi really hates comedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnJust The Way You Are\pos(205.057,152)\frz13.5\frx20\fs38\fry325\c&HB4B2BE&\3c&H343855&\bord4\be4}Open
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\bord1.5\blur0.5\fs50\frz363\fnVerdana\fad(450,0)\c&H4394ED&\pos(195.994,325)}Radio Gaga
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnDupree\fs24\pos(453.165,279)\frz348.5\frx13\fry30\bord0\c&H443128&\blur0.5}Southern
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:23.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fnDupree\fs24\pos(461.095,310)\frz349\frx13\fry30\bord0\c&H443128&\blur0.5}Wind
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.65,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I heard that guys from\NCromartie come here often.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:29.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's catch them quickly\N and put the squeeze on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:30.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.66,0:06:33.99,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It'd be dangerous, since\N this place is in their territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.99,0:06:35.16,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Destrade High School has at last turned\Ntheir blade against Cromartie High School!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.99,0:06:36.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Let's hear Yamaguchi's, our leader's, idea first.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is the very moment in which\Ntheir battle will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:41.63,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\be2\pos(358,392)}Noboru Yamaguchi (16)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.25,0:06:41.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\pos(358,478)}And Noboru Yamaguchi, leader\Nof Des-High Year 1, was thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:46.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,about how to change this\Nheavy mood to comedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.05,0:06:51.26,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.5\bord1.2\pos(353.468,395)\shad2}Yamaguchi's coffee
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I really don't have time for this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.22,0:06:51.26,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I have to go home soon and work on the postcards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:55.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,His secret hobby is\N sending jokes in to radio shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,At any rate, I'm a "postcard artisan"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:01.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,who currently contributes\N to seven late-night radio shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.40,0:07:05.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,There are many listeners\N who look forward to my jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:10.03,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's no exaggeration to say that those shows\Ndon't start unless I write those postcards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:13.62,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Last night, they even used five of my postcards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.91,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Since it was five out of seven cards,\Nmy batting average is so-so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:21.25,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,By the way, my pen name is\N "Ajishio Taro," and I like it myself too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:25.92,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But there is only one thing\N that this "Ajishio Taro" doesn't like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:28.51,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:33.14,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,To hell with Cro-High!\NWe'll beat up Takenouchi good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.31,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wanna bust some heads soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.81,0:07:40.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi's getting furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.10,0:07:42.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I'm getting fired up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.77,0:07:46.57,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,That there is another postcard\Nartisan who surpasses even me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.57,0:07:49.19,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,His name is "Honey Boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.19,0:07:52.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,The next one is by pen name Mr. "Honey Boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:56.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,His postcards always get read\Nat the most critical times.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.87,0:08:01.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Honey Boy, the only postcard artisan\Nwhose sense of humor I acknowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.54,0:08:07.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Anyways, unless I exceed him,\NI can't sleep peacefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.21,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi is troubled by something.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:13.22,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He must be worried, since\Nwe're going up against Cro-High.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:17.18,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,While I'm sitting here doing nothing,\N"Honey Boy" must be cranking out new jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.18,0:08:20.39,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Actually, my hobby is sending\N jokes in to late-night radio shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.10,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You're pretty dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.10,0:08:23.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.31,0:08:27.06,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Are you possibly using\Na pen name or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:28.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:32.11,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I thought of it\N by accident in the kitchen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.11,0:08:33.45,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,It's "Honey Boy."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.33,0:08:43.00,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Then what kind of jokes are you writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:46.63,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Well, in fact, I thought of\Na pretty good joke this week.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:50.80,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's "Honey Boy"!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:54.05,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And he's also gonna\Nannounce a pretty good joke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:56.01,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Yamaguchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He's really concerned\Nabout the guys behind him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:03.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Those two... They're wearing\NCro-High's uniform...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.02,0:09:03.85,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.85,0:09:06.98,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't get excited. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hey, let me see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.94,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,No way, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.03,0:09:15.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me Yamaguchi is scared of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.82,0:09:17.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are those two?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.62,0:09:21.08,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You screwed up, Honey Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.37,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,You don't even know Ajishio Taro is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:25.66,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Quit acting so arrogant, tell it to me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.70,0:09:26.54,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,This is a once in a lifetime chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:29.46,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If others hear it, I'll get embarrassed,\Nso I'll tell you in a whisper, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:39.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Yamaguchi is sliding down little by little, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.97,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What the hell is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:44.64,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I can't understand him at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.48,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,So that's the joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.10,0:09:49.36,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I see! That kind of joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.23,0:09:52.40,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's head back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.61,0:09:55.32,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Even though we haven't fought yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.32,0:09:57.61,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,More like, what did we come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:04.12,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Honey Boy, you meet your end today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.12,0:10:07.87,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I sent your joke in by express mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.87,0:10:10.67,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Hear it and be dumbfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:14.09,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Next is our popular corner; "Puns by Postcard!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.09,0:10:16.76,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Today's theme is\N"something that happened at school."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.76,0:10:19.43,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,We'll start with our regular, Mr. "Ajishio Taro."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.43,0:10:23.68,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,He sent another one in.\NMake us laugh again tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.52,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,But there's just one thing that I'm worried about.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:29.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.73,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,"I ate pork cutlet yesterday with a 'cut'\Nof the money that I extorted."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.49,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,What a dud.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.99,0:10:41.82,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.07,0:10:43.70,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,And he even delivered it by express mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:45.01,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\alpha130\fs24\fnNeon\bord0\c&H4E1728&\blur0.5\pos(346.671,139)}Next\N\N\N\NEpisode
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.5\fnArial Black\bord3\c&H000000&\3c&HFBFAFC&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Typeset,,0,0,0,,{\shad0\fs26\blur0.6\fnArial Black\bord3.2\c&H000000&\3c&H3F3F3F&\pos(203.924,50)}Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.01,0:11:50.02,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial Black\fs36\bord2.2\blur0.5\pos(540.399,465)}Wait for the\N\N\N next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:37.17,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,Dear Mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:41.59,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,I wanted to ask Maeda about "Sakigake!!\NCromartie High School's" next episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,but it seems that he's not around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.56,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(45.316,470)}Is it my turn?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.47,Dialogue etc,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(45.316,470)}Please calm down, Takenouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(213.928,323.39)}When you are watching television
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:07.32,Intro Warning,,0,0,0,,{\fs23\blur0.3\pos(587.096,341.559)}please have the room\Nbrightly lit and be\Ncareful not to get too\Nclose to the screen.
